title: In the Heart of Pleasanton Close to Everything you Will Need!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Pleasanton Place Apartments Homes!', 'Pleasanton Place has a relaxed and joyful exterior.', 'Enjoy the beautifully maintained grounds and lay out at our meticulously kept pool.', 'Have a dinner under the stars in our BBQ and picnic area designed for your family to enjoy.', '- 2 On-site Community Laundry Centers', '- $0 Deposit Community', '- Professional management', '- Picnic area with barbeque', '- Near major Tri-Valley employment centers, shopping, dining & entertainment', '- Easy access to BART, ACE Train, I-680 and I-580', '- Assigned covered parking', '- Pool with sun deck', '- Award winning Pleasanton school district', '- Many options to pay rent including credit card and ACH', '- Resident referral program', '- 10-minute walk from historical Downtown Pleasanton', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.', 'Property Code PP:ESR3609']
